1.0.2.name: wordpress/idx-broker-platinum
1.0.2.description:
IDX Broker Platinum Plugin

  • Plans start at $59.99 and are well-suited to Offices and tech-savvy Realtors. For plans that start at $39.99, check out the IDX Broker Original Plugin.
  • Intra-daily updates for all RETS datasets (check with your local MLS), for the most up-to-date data and images.
  • New Layout Selector, with impressive new layouts that can be selected for each page type.
  • Custom Domains setup through IDX Broker Platinum are fully indexable according to Google. Choosing a hosted solution like IDX Broker Platinum means that you will get many more lead capture,
